title: Marmalade Live Seattle Music 6.26.2005
description:
This torrent (marmalade_live_seattle_music_6.26.2005.torrent) contains the live recorded show of Seattle&#039;s Marmalade performing at L&#039;Intermediaire in Marseilles, France on June 26, 2005.

The Marmaladians that night were:
Funk Love - vocals
Kimo Muraki - vocals, alto sax, and guitar
Big Talk Jon Ryser - alto sax
Brian StingShark Ray - guitar, vocals
Buddhaful Mike - keyboards
Chad Redlight - drum kit
Tyrone "LBD" Lovelace - bass

The show was recorded directly to digital on Buddhaful Mike&#039;s computer. (He ran out of space and didn&#039;t get the whole show - so sad!) Find out more about Buddhaful at http://www.Buddhaful.com

The set that was recorded has been cut up into 4 mp3&#039;s (44.1 Khz, stereo, 192 kbps).

All songs were written and performed by Marmalade and the afore mentioned Marmaladians.
